iface eth0 inet static
address 192.168.1.5
netmask 255.255.255.0
gateway 192.168.1.254


Setup interface to dhcp

To setup eth0 to dhcp, enter:
auto eth0
iface eth0 inet dhcp

 sudo service networking restart



